學習規範 Course Policy
1. 上課不能玩手遊, 可使用手機上網查資料及字典, 可轉靜音以便接緊急電話, 以不影響老師及同學上課文原則.
2. 功課準時交;
3. 盡量說英文;
4. 沒有假單, 不予補考;
5. 考試作弊或不把非應試用品收起來(如手機及鉛筆盒), 一律零分;
6. 以email請任何假無效, 請依學校規定請假.
1. No playing games on cell phone and no disturbance to either teacher or other classmates; 
2. Hand in your homework on time;
3. Speak English as much as you can;
4. No sick/event leave sheet, no make-up test;
5. Cheating in any ways--0 points.
6. Emailing to ask for event/sick leaves DOESN'T COUNT!! Please obey the school regulations. 


