最佳解答: 
             useful early childhood assessment:play-based,interviews and multiple 
intelligences 
對童年初期實用的評價方式: 玩耍基礎下, 面談和多方面的才智 
Some types of early childhood assessment focus on the evaluation of children in their natural, everyday settings such as the home, day care, or preschool center.  
有些對童年初期的評價類型著重在孩子的性格, 家裡, 托兒所等平日的環境, 或是幼稚園 
Information obtained from these assessments can be functional because it identifies skills for intervention that will be immediately useful for young children with special needs and their families.  
這些經評估所得到的資訊是實用的, 因為對有特別需要的小孩子及他們的家庭是立即且有效的的評估技巧 

This article describes three types of functional assessment: play-based, family interviews, and the evaluation of multiple intelligences.  
這篇文章描述了三種實用的評估方式: 玩耍基礎下, 家庭訪問和對多方面的才智的評估 

All three types are useful for planning developmentally appropriate interventions and are positive because the emphasis is more on the children's and their families' strengths rather than on their weaknesses.  
這三種類型對規畫啟發性的適當乾預是有用的且正面的, 因為重點是在兒童和他們家庭的優點而不是在他們的弱點。 
Keyword: Useful early childhood assessment 
關鍵詞: 對童年初期實用的評價方式 




